data.title: Pulse Memorial Advisory Committee Meeting
data.meta_description:
The Pulse Memorial Advisory Committee, consisting of families, survivors and other community stakeholders, was created to guide engagement toward the recommendation of a conceptual design for a permanent memorial to the Orlando City Council by the end of this year.

Open House to follow Committee Meeting from 6:00 PM - 8:00PM

For info on virtual attendance, visit pulseorlando.org.
